---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About EmailToolsGuide"
  description="Learn about our mission to provide honest, unbiased email marketing software reviews and comparisons."
>
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">About EmailToolsGuide</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none prose-a:text-primary">
      <p>
        EmailToolsGuide is an independent review site dedicated to helping businesses, bloggers, and creators find the right email marketing software.
      </p>

      <h2>Our Process</h2>
      <p>
        Every tool we review is tested hands-on. We create real accounts, set up real campaigns, and evaluate each platform on ease of use, features, deliverability, pricing, and customer support.
      </p>

      <h2>How We Make Money</h2>
      <p>
        Some of our links are affiliate links, meaning we earn a commission when you sign up through them. This comes at no extra cost to you and helps us keep the site running. Our editorial opinions are never influenced by affiliate partnerships — if a tool isn't good, we'll say so.
      </p>

      <h2>Our Promise</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Honest, unbiased reviews based on real testing</li>
        <li>Clear disclosure of affiliate relationships</li>
        <li>Regular updates to keep reviews current</li>
        <li>Transparent rating methodology</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
